Description: Professional package for spatial analysis of fish consumption patterns
    across Senegalese regions. Provides tools for geospatial data integration,
    statistical mapping, hotspot detection, and interactive visualization.
    Designed for researchers and policy analysts working on food security
    and fisheries management.
